      <title>甘茨政党提议投票解散以色列议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/gantz-s-party-proposes-vote-to-dissolve-israel-s-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨的政党表示，希望解散议会，以迫使提前举行选举并罢免总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/gantz-s-party-proposes-vote-to-dissolve-israel-s-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 14:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
